### **2. 33_APINodeScanner**  
**Description:**  
Scans API nodes across environments and logs health metrics in real time.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APINodeScanner - Distributed API Health Tracker

APINodeScanner helps monitor multi-node deployments by checking latency and HTTP status of each target.

## Features
- Multi-node tracking  
- Export to JSON or CSV  
- Latency heatmap support  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/33_APINodeScanner.git
cd 33_APINodeScanner
python monitor.py
